
Iris lives in Pennsylvania with her mom and dad,but once she finds out she is adopted she has the choice of moving to living on the farm she inherited after her biological mother died or staying with mom and dad.Make a choice will not only affect her future but her family , the animals that live on the farm and someone else she mets.If she does move to her mothers farm how will she learn how to adjust and what if she changes her mind what will happen then?
